headline: UDR price target raised to $51 from $49 at Scotiabank
summary: Scotiabank raised the firm’s price target on UDR (UDR) to $51 from $49 and keeps a Sector Perform rating on the shares. The firm is adjusting its estimates on U.S. Real Estate & REITs in its coverage following Q1 results, the analyst tells investors. Quarterly results contained some negative surprises, but generally played out as expected, with most companies maintaining FY25 guidance, the firm notes.
